_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E8%94%A1%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%92%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E8%94%A1%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%92%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E8%94%A1%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%92%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E8%94%A1%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%92%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E8%94%A1%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%92%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E8%94%A1%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%92%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_log=Y&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1980-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1989-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D | dead-url=no }}</ref>，香港已故影星，生於[[廣東|廣東]][[興寧市|興寧]]，籍貫廣東[[新會|新會]]，有「奇女子」之稱。狄娜与[[白韻琹|白韻琹]]、[[俞琤|俞琤]]和[[林燕妮|林燕妮]]等皆獲得“香江才女”的美譽。

